{"tid":1569900,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人可以幫下手","createTime":"2019-09-14T19:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T20:23:55.000Z","uid":310712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9a0029005ae6595572a847a5495e694e3292c946","tid":1569900,"uid":310712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:33:07.000Z","msg":"小妹我唔小心上Facebook睇新聞時click開左昨晚fb那張「自殺」女子既分屍圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實經過呢三個月，我而家情緒真係好脆弱，個下就快喊出理<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打算上連登睇下有無最新情況，點知一打開唔夠30秒又睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實完全唔打格既相真係好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能會有絲打巴打覺得小妹我睇多幾次就唔驚，但其實我驚到而家都瞓唔到（應該過了4小時左右）<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇絲打巴打知道我應該點算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住對唔住對唔住但我真係好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c43d29e37e971f3e1feaf49b0835c5c8641c48","tid":1569900,"uid":201992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:34:07.000Z","msg":"傾下計？"},{"pid":"e29fd5b0bda90bb89442cf8433dd892babf7b1e7","tid":1569900,"uid":310712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:35:57.000Z","msg":"小妹我啱啱先入到大學拿到isp email註冊連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有咩用字太奇怪對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望真係有絲打巴打可以幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a2cab9de372cd6c23a4fd0373327fa630fdaeb","tid":1569900,"uid":310712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50c43d29e37e971f3e1feaf49b0835c5c8641c48","tid":1569900,"uid":201992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:34:07.000Z","msg":"傾下計？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T19:37:06.000Z","msg":"多謝你應我<img src=\"/asset